what are their lives like

00:02:14.434 --> 00:02:15.935
without each other?

00:02:15.935 --> 00:02:17.270
- Yeah, their lives would
suck without each other.

00:02:17.270 --> 00:02:19.706 align:start size:84% position:16%
- We added some stuff.
- Yeah.

00:02:20.874 --> 00:02:22.208
- Hey.

00:02:22.208 --> 00:02:24.210
- What we were trying to
say is that inevitably

00:02:24.210 --> 00:02:26.513 align:start size:97% position:3%
these two would've found each
other and become friends.

00:02:26.513 --> 00:02:28.648
- Some people you're
just destined to meet

00:02:28.648 --> 00:02:29.883
and fall in love with.

00:02:29.883 --> 00:02:32.552
(both laughing)

